# VugaLink - Professional Language Services Website

## Overview
VugaLink Ltd is Rwanda's premier language service company providing real-time virtual interpretation, on-site interpretation, document translation, transcription, and data input services. We bridge language gaps for expatriates, tourists, NGOs, and businesses across Rwanda.

## 🌟 Key Features

### Language Services
- **Virtual Interpretation**: Real-time remote interpretation services
- **On-Site Interpretation**: Professional interpreters for events and meetings
- **Document Translation**: Multi-language document translation services
- **Transcription Services**: Audio/video to text conversion
- **Data Input & Typing**: Professional data entry services
- **Language Consultation**: Expert language guidance and support

### Website Features
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach for all devices
- **Multi-language Support**: Kinyarwanda, English, French
- **Contact Forms**: Easy quote requests and inquiries
- **Service Gallery**: Visual showcase of our capabilities
- **Professional UI/UX**: Modern, clean interface design

## 🚀 WhatsApp Integration

### Floating WhatsApp Button
- **Delayed Appearance**: Button appears after 40 seconds for better user experience
- **Professional Design**: Expert-looking floating button with smooth animations
- **Direct Contact**: One-click access to WhatsApp chat using number: +250788376668
- **Responsive**: Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices

### Button Features
- Smooth fade-in animation after 40 seconds
- Bouncing animation to attract attention
- Hover effects with tooltip
- Mobile-responsive sizing
- High z-index for proper layering

