## 🔧 WhatsApp Button Implementation

### CSS Classes
- `.whatsapp-float`: Main container positioning
- `.whatsapp-icon`: Button styling and animations
- `.whatsapp-tooltip`: Hover tooltip display
- `.show`: Animation trigger class

### JavaScript Functionality
```javascript
// Show WhatsApp button after 40 seconds
setTimeout(function() {
    const whatsappButton = document.getElementById('whatsapp-button');
    if (whatsappButton) {
        whatsappButton.style.display = 'block';
        whatsappButton.classList.add('show');
    }
}, 40000); // 40 seconds
```

