## 🚀 Getting Started

### Local Development
1. Clone the repository
2. Open any HTML file in a modern web browser
3. The WhatsApp button will appear after 40 seconds
4. Test responsive design using browser dev tools

### Customization
- Modify WhatsApp number in HTML files
- Adjust button appearance in CSS
- Change timing in JavaScript
- Update content and images as needed

